# @samuelho-dev/infra-cache

Cache orchestration infrastructure (coordinates cache providers)

## Overview

This infrastructure library provides service implementations.

## Contents

- **Service**: Core service implementation
- **Providers**: Service providers and adapters
- **Configuration**: Service configuration

## Usage

```typescript
import { /* service */ } from '@samuelho-dev/infra-cache';
```

## Development

```bash
# Build
nx build infra-cache

# Test
nx test infra-cache
```
